  "slug": "chocolate-hazelnut-stuffed-cookies",
  "title": "Chocolate hazelnut stuffed cookies",
  "subtitle": "A spoon of chocolate hazelnut spread frozen into the centre of each cookie.",
  "excerpt": "Chocolate hazelnut stuffed cookies. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook, a recipe she's made many times in her own kitchen.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Chocolate hazelnut stuffed cookies. An American family-table recipe, generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Serves 20.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cookies bake fast and reward a chilled dough. Pull them out when the edges set and the middles still look slightly underdone.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
